Plot: The Wheel of Time turns, and Ages come and go. What was, what will be, and what is, may yet fall under the Shadow. Let the Dragon ride again on the winds of time.
Characters: Rand al'Thor, Nynaeve al'Meara, Egwene al'Vere, Perrin Aybara, Matrim Cauthon, Min Farshaw, Elayne Trakand, Aviendha, Siuan Sanche, Birgitte Silverbow
